2. Add custom font imports (Inter or similar modern sans-serif)
3. Configure shadcn/ui theme to use dark mode by default
4. Set up spacing scale and typography hierarchy
5. Create CSS custom properties for consistent gold/amber gradients

1. Install Framer Motion:
```bash
npm install framer-motion
```

2. Initialize and install shadcn/ui components needed:
```bash
npx shadcn@latest init
npx shadcn@latest add button card input textarea form dialog dropdown-menu tabs avatar badge progress skeleton separator scroll-area
```

